  "summary": {
    "title": "Professional Summary",
    "columns": 1,
    "hidden": false,
    "content": "<p><strong>Technology & Product Leader</strong> with an <strong>MBA from IIM Trichy</strong> and 12+ years of experience bridging the gap between <strong>Engineering Execution</strong> and <strong>Business Strategy</strong>. Expert in launching <strong>AI-Native Products</strong>, designing scalable platforms for regulated markets (RegTech), and driving cost-efficient delivery through open-source adoption. Proven track record of architecting solutions that reduce technical debt by <strong>85%</strong> and accelerating time-to-market by <strong>60%</strong> through hands-on prototyping. Experienced in zero-to-one launches, international expansion strategy, and transforming legacy systems into modern revenue engines.</p>"
  },
